    "en": {
      "title": "Indian players meet Sri Lankan fans",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former captain of Indian cricket team Virat Kohli and Rohit Sharma met disabled Sri Lankan cricket fan Kayan Senanayake.",
        "The 2022 Asia Cup series is currently being held in Dubai. According to this, yesterday (28) the match between India and Pakistan teams took place.",
        "Virat Kohli and Rohit Sharma met Gayan Senanayake the day after this match took place (29).",
        "Meanwhile, Gayan Senanayake was also attending Virat Kohli's wedding reception. (a)"
      ],
